{"tid":55193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"信我屈機男，大家食真係好野來嫁","createTime":"2016-12-26T08:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-03T18:37:21.000Z","uid":40470,"like":13,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98bfe2c43864d20193094d67273b7ee8bb0bb268","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"試一次，ok?<br />\n<br />\n最緊要唔好去錯"},{"pid":"ad38a3361fc8102f21f12b9b3f001be4938968e3","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc4/41784_7533757190_9569_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprofile.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhprofile-ak-snc4%2F41784_7533757190_9569_n.jpg&h=59507a69&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同呂以村先生傾過計<br />\n<br />\n我dup 低頭食緊十三會手攪面時<br />\n<br />\n見到隔離有人影企左起度<br />\n<br />\n一抬頭<br />\n<br />\n原來係呂以村先生<br />\n<br />\n佢望住我笑咪咪<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點好<br />\n<br />\n就同佢講<br />\n<br />\n你d面好好食呀！<br />\n<br />\n佢好客氣咁講<br />\n<br />\n多謝，多謝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n佢一直企起度望住我食完為止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c1a3b6e311fa26c44425b9de69c7a88f2e96d8","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"你入呂以村先生間舖<br />\n<br />\n門面，招牌<br />\n<br />\n的確係好柒<br />\n<br />\n但你會見到每一細節<br />\n<br />\n確係花過心機<br />\n<br />\n由餐牌，牆身呂以村先生既介紹<br />\n<br />\n你都睇到熱誠認真"},{"pid":"df0a60ffe325b16f16cc22c4b79c415a346399e2","tid":55193,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"佢心諗 食唔晒就用把金槍射死你"},{"pid":"7124799486e68309feea5d0c36f0bfa292423636","tid":55193,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你入呂以村先生間舖<br />\n<br />\n門面，招牌<br />\n<br />\n的確係好柒<br />\n<br />\n但你會見到每一細節<br />\n<br />\n確係花過心機<br />\n<br />\n由餐牌，牆身呂以村先生既介紹<br />\n<br />\n你都睇到熱誠認真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見你呢段 有啲想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d74eb5e1a4e0082804303d59e545108dabfa9cc","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:07:00.000Z","msg":"今時今日<br />\n<br />\n你去連鎖餐廳見到d後生仔女waiter<br />\n<br />\n你會見到佢'挨'返工既態度<br />\n<br />\n唔想做，但為份糧<br />\n<br />\n去到大家食<br />\n<br />\n個個都係呀姐級waiter<br />\n<br />\n雖然都係為份糧打工<br />\n<br />\n但你見到佢地既踏實，盡心盡力<br />\n<br />\n真心去做好大家食<br />\n<br />\n我真心尊敬呂以村先生既打拼事蹟<br />\n<br />\n靠雙手，靠勤力<br />\n<br />\n開創自己事業"},{"pid":"d9e0cec80c3c78bd8c29161326321f2fee858519","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"男人大丈夫<br />\n<br />\n就算只係一次都好<br />\n<br />\n應該去試下食大家食<br />\n<br />\n除左醫肚外感受下一間食店<br />\n<br />\n老闆開舖既心血，熱誠<br />\n<br />\n好多年輕人怨天尤人，嘆今時今日時不我予，工作毫用心<br />\n<br />\n但你請睇下一個無學歷（斗膽假設，講錯我會道歉）既大叔靠雙手打拼出來既成就<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生有好多比年輕人學習既地方<br />\n<br />\n去大家食食一餐食飽之餘，體驗下成功既要領"},{"pid":"0e8aadf5418b0309babff3de4ac4d25150b2707f","tid":55193,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"正式宣布屈蛇姓呂"},{"pid":"bae1aa521c9a4118e42657b0b73005d83229bbd0","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"食物品質味道水準極高<br />\n<br />\n再引入風韻猶存靚女做侍應<br />\n<br />\n新裝修超高格調<br />\n<br />\n但價錢不變"},{"pid":"99eb2545608ffc0f014b16c261248ef9268845a8","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"我認為呂以村先生既才能勁過肯德基伯伯<br />\n<br />\n肯德基伯伯淨係識整雞<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生才華洋溢<br />\n<br />\n識整手攪面，村村住家窩面，過山雞，滷大腸，十三會<br />\n<br />\n求其一種都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n相比肯德基淨係識整雞"},{"pid":"44cb043356b73a7bde51e13fd44c0d723382cf51","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"而我認為除非譚仔同佢三哥聯手<br />\n<br />\n否則呂以村先生單打獨鬥下必輕取二人"},{"pid":"00589706a48b2bc3f4453fa182d3d8d07e53ca0d","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"呂以村先生贏過食神挑戰賽第二<br />\n<br />\n你可能話，<br />\n<br />\n點解贏唔到第一？<br />\n<br />\n因為呂先生既大絕手攪面當年仲未完成<br />\n<br />\n如今呂先生既手攪面已經獨霸美食界<br />\n<br />\n每條面都用捕獲等級4200既奇蹟小麥精製<br />\n<br />\n手攪面以呂先生既80G臂力攪成<br />\n<br />\n其QQ程度無法抗拒"},{"pid":"7cbc63070e07d718e73bc634d109ece9bf5fb132","tid":55193,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"捕獲等級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5515aa4e2bebb6ed705daf6fd81f481d5e3e421d","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"每次步入大家食<br />\n<br />\n我必先淨身<br />\n<br />\n帶著感恩敬佩之心<br />\n<br />\n斗膽地去order酸辣十三會手攪面走芽菜<br />\n<br />\n我只有三十五之齡<br />\n<br />\n卻能有幸品嚐千年難得之美食<br />\n<br />\n十三會，每一會都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n肉菜均衡<br />\n<br />\n請容我續一介紹："},{"pid":"9e5d536eda9a09b79bc85fff23dd7afa6f0045ee","tid":55193,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"細過食過，又平又大碗，可惜唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0395fe53170371a576f8e4bccb4a20a2836cbb76","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"蘿蔔，甜美可口<br />\n<br />\n吸收左美味湯汁，再混和蘿蔔本身味道<br />\n<br />\n人間極品"},{"pid":"b89571001b62634a29697736f53e8521a5bea45b","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"腩肉，肥瘦相隔<br />\n<br />\n放在舌尖上<br />\n<br />\n油脂溶化，瘦肉有咬口<br />\n<br />\n兩者就像太極之道<br />\n<br />\n相生相克<br />\n<br />\n味道之中感悟人生大道理"},{"pid":"05f691f02500956128ec7a83a74615c40d212e23","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"過山雞，聽聞呢味菜係呂先生人生第一次玩過山車時諗出來既<br />\n<br />\n食過山雞尤似坐過山車<br />\n<br />\n時而平穩，時而刺激<br />\n<br />\n過山雞外層略脆味濃<br />\n<br />\n刺激味覺神經<br />\n<br />\n內裡肉質鮮嫩多汁<br />\n<br />\n味道穩健充實<br />\n<br />\n每次食過山雞<br />\n<br />\n必然回想起人生跌盪<br />\n<br />\n亦想起呂先生沉實敦厚既外型"},{"pid":"b7a547531fbf649c318b63179492458ce3560c1d","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"大家見面大家食<br />\n<br />\n大家食面見大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記住<br />\n<br />\n無呂以村先生人像商標<br />\n<br />\n果間唔係真既大家食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一次不來你錯過<br />\n<br />\n兩次不來我過錯<br />\n<br />\n來吧<br />\n<br />\n怕去食大家食"},{"pid":"dfbea4e68ee72d86c3b18ff29a48be7ee4f1f484","tid":55193,"uid":24648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢心諗 食唔晒就用把金槍射死你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1ff8025af6925fd79d6f0eba8e1092231ca266","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"一齊去食啦"},{"pid":"49e90817f8083f8249604ab8b015799f5911e8be","tid":55193,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"大家食都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過幾次<br />\n第一次食覺得好正<br />\n跟住再去食次次都覺得咸撚到仆街<br />\n都唔知第一次點解覺得好食"},{"pid":"d9adc4806607bc63749948c487156373981eb398","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家食都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過幾次<br />\n第一次食覺得好正<br />\n跟住再去食次次都覺得咸撚到仆街<br />\n都唔知第一次點解覺得好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去錯喇<br />\n<br />\n有呂先生頭像先係正舖"},{"pid":"10608bddbfae76ffc46c2a10e2f3be33