ockquote><blockquote>信你老母 萬五都拎唔到出黎既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n有錢一定要拎出來？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個賭局你開架 柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9904d5f89b70ba0a20c7361cc78c43390aa51d","tid":55193,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"死垃圾俾米已成炊收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871fbd719cc7c45f0753020e2db225c04537e66b","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>信你老母 萬五都拎唔到出黎既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n有錢一定要拎出來？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個賭局你開架 柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我開我就要玩落去？<br />\n<br />\n我目的係局佢捐得多過我又戇鳩拍片唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d423595506597f19e8ee22f0047a5de5d21cbe","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf019e1c4f40c852b1af8ac5c2701439fa93c3f3","tid":55193,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:39:55.000Z","msg":"咩最好食"},{"pid":"aa818846e91d95a1e3bd4004b75f65cee165b371","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩最好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手就試下手攪面加自己鍾意既餸<br />\n<br />\n麻辣同酸辣底都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa1a215f8982a888834ae7ba24ecc537338fb48","tid":55193,"uid":60372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每次步入大家食<br />\n<br />\n我必先淨身<br />\n<br />\n帶著感恩敬佩之心<br />\n<br />\n斗膽地去order酸辣十三會手攪面<span style=\"color: red;\">走芽菜</span><br />\n<br />\n我只有三十五之齡<br />\n<br />\n卻能有幸品嚐千年難得之美食<br />\n<br />\n十三會，每一會都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n肉菜均衡<br />\n<br />\n請容我續一介紹：</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解你要拒絕呂以村先生精心為你預備的芽菜?</blockquote><br />\n逃避問題？"},{"pid":"acf8816a9fde662ab632fa175aa344c9093b8407","tid":55193,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:23:01.000Z","msg":"屈蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49973410421fd91e4ca4ea30f7bfadbf13af1849","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每次步入大家食<br />\n<br />\n我必先淨身<br />\n<br />\n帶著感恩敬佩之心<br />\n<br />\n斗膽地去order酸辣十三會手攪面<span style=\"color: red;\">走芽菜</span><br />\n<br />\n我只有三十五之齡<br />\n<br />\n卻能有幸品嚐千年難得之美食<br />\n<br />\n十三會，每一會都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n肉菜均衡<br />\n<br />\n請容我續一介紹：</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解你要拒絕呂以村先生精心為你預備的芽菜?</blockquote><br />\n逃避問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我認為芽菜有礙手攪面口感<br />\n<br />\n但上次見個地盤佬大口大口<br />\n<br />\n面連芽菜食到索索聲好粗豪<br />\n<br />\n你可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4181f9bc526c3b028c30de90834420ddefb8884","tid":55193,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屈蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無介紹錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dae0d3d01c480bb2bbbcd9e89370442482b039c","tid":55193,"uid":60372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:41:21.000Z","msg":"等佢屯元